	* Makefile.PL: bug 1652: the suggested patch doesn't work.  perl
	5.6.0 and perl 5.6.1 both have EU:MM 5.45, but the one in 5.6.1 has
	PM_FILTER.  so reverting the initial patch since it doesn't take
	this into account.

