2002-10-22 20:11  jmason

	* MANIFEST, MANIFEST.SKIP, Makefile.PL, README, sa-forget.raw,
	sa-learn-nonspam.raw, sa-learn-spam.raw, lib/Mail/SpamAssassin.pm,
